videos.description: Vernon Carey Jr. cleans up his teammate's miss, sticks with it and hits a tough layup under pressure in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Duke's Carey jams amid two Georgetown defenders) 2019/11/22

videos.headline: Duke's Carey jams amid two Georgetown defenders

videos.description: The Hoyas force a turnover allowing Jagan Mosely and Galen Alexander to rush the ball down court for a nice layup vs. Duke.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Alexander flies down the court for slick basket) 2019/11/22

videos.headline: Alexander flies down the court for slick basket

videos.description: Vernon Carey Jr. posts up late in the first half to knot the game up at 31-31 vs. Georgetown.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Carey flushes it home for Duke) 2019/11/22

videos.headline: Carey flushes it home for Duke

videos.description: James Akinjo gets through multiple Duke defenders and puts up a tough jumper in the final seconds of the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Akinjo's clutch jumper ties it up before half) 2019/11/22

videos.headline: Akinjo's clutch jumper ties it up before half

videos.description: Cassius Stanley impresses with an acrobatic move to catch Tre Jones' inbounds pass and lay it in.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Stanley shows off his athleticism with jam off the inbounds) 2019/11/22

videos.headline: Stanley shows off his athleticism with jam off the inbounds

videos.description: Josh LeBlanc picks off the Duke pass and brings the ball up to the hoop for a powerful slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (LeBlanc steals and slams for Georgetown) 2019/11/22

videos.headline: LeBlanc steals and slams for Georgetown

videos.description: Georgetown coach Patrick Ewing rushes onto the court in disagreement over a foul call and receives a technical in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Ewing argues with refs, gets technical foul) 2019/11/22

videos.headline: Ewing argues with refs, gets technical foul
